OL,3,CVeterans given rent rises despite
OL,4,Cbeing unable to go home for 10 months
OL,6,FJersey war veterans say they have been
OL,7,Flet down as many are waiting for their
OL,8,Fproperties to be made livable again
OL,9,Ffollowing the impact of Storm Ciaran.
OL,11,FAround a dozen former members of the
OL,12,FArmed Services are still staying in
OL,13,Ftemporary accommodation, 10 months
OL,14,Fsince the storm swept across the
OL,15,FChannel Islands.
OL,17,FNow they have been told their rent is
OL,18,Fgoing up, despite being unable to move
OL,19,Fhome.
