OL,4,Cbeing unable to go home for 10 months
OL,6,FThe storm battered the islands in
OL,7,Fearly November 2023 and saw 121 Jersey
OL,8,Fresidents evacuated from their homes.
OL,10,FWind speeds hit up to 186mph in
OL,11,FJersey, devastating properties and
OL,12,Fprompting a red 'threat to life' alert
OL,13,Ffrom the island's Met Office.
OL,15,FExperts later confirmed that Jersey
OL,16,Fwas struck by a "significant tornado",
OL,17,Fbelieved to be the largest in the
OL,18,FBritish Isles since 1954.
