OL,3,CVeterans given rent rises despite
OL,4,Cbeing unable to go home for 10 months
OL,6,FSince then, management groups have
OL,7,Fbeen working on fixing residents'
OL,8,Fhomes but The Haig Housing Trust for
OL,9,Fservice personnel and their families
OL,10,Fare among the last to get it sorted.
OL,12,FResident Barbara Gilliard lives in one
OL,13,Fof the areas most affected and is
OL,14,Fconcerned with the lack of progress.
OL,16,FShe explains: "What I'm frightened of
OL,17,Fis if we get more storms like we did
OL,18,Flast winter, they have patched us up
OL,19,Fso we will have no rain coming in but
OL,20,Fall of that is going out the window."
