OL,3,CVeterans given rent rises despite
OL,4,Cbeing unable to go home for 10 months
OL,6,FBarbara also says there have been rent
OL,7,Fincreases since the storm which she
OL,8,Fcalls "a bit of kick in the teeth".
OL,10,FVeteran Nigel Smith explains: "Excuses
OL,11,Fare wearing a little bit thin. I know
OL,12,Fthere are problems with contractors,
OL,13,Fthere will be problems with pricing
OL,14,Fand insurance, but there are other
OL,15,Fhouses that are similarly damaged and
OL,16,Fare now repaired."
OL,18,FThe Royal British Legion has been
OL,19,Fproviding support for veterans in
OL,20,FJersey who have been displaced.
