OL,6,F"We have always said we want to get
OL,7,Fthose individuals back into their
OL,8,Fhomes by the end of October and we
OL,9,Fthink we are still on target for that."
OL,11,FThe Trust adds that its rents are
OL,12,Fstill lower than most.
